2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a reinforcement learning-based controller, which is a subfield of AI. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the control of a quadcopter system, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a neural network-based propeller fault detection system, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not the main focus of the paper, computer vision techniques may be used in the propeller fault detection system.
